1531:
WITH TopSpender AS (
    SELECT CustomerID, SUM(Price) AS TotalSpent
    FROM transactions_1k
    GROUP BY CustomerID
    ORDER BY TotalSpent DESC
    LIMIT 1
)
SELECT ts.CustomerID, ts.TotalSpent, c.Currency, CAST(ts.TotalSpent / COUNT(DISTINCT p.ProductID) AS REAL) AS AvgPricePerItem
FROM TopSpender ts
JOIN customers c ON ts.CustomerID = c.CustomerID
JOIN transactions_1k t ON ts.CustomerID = t.CustomerID
JOIN products p ON t.ProductID = p.ProductID
GROUP BY ts.CustomerID, c.Currency
ORDER BY ts.TotalSpent DESC
LIMIT 1;
